{"tid":1327820,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"查比亞去馬體會","createTime":"2019-07-17T17:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T02:33:17.000Z","uid":234509,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"4721f93948f4cc8d0f8dc6740b81d096d7b07e11","tid":1327820,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d96f8e03916c98bafabe10685be1f07f93ccb12","tid":1327820,"uid":2607,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:51:44.000Z","msg":"廢到咁都有得踢下體"},{"pid":"bd9d69353d0fd99a068a86bff1379bceae141051","tid":1327820,"uid":234509,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:52:17.000Z","msg":"查比亞將加盟馬體會<br />\n　　據英國權威媒體《BBC》的報導，熱刺右閘查比亞（K.Trippier）接近完成轉會，他將加盟西甲的馬德里體育會隊，轉會費為2000萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n　　查比亞現年28歲，他是在2015年從般尼轉會球隊的，已經為熱刺累計出場過百場，也踢了今年的歐聯決賽。他與熱刺的合約要到2022年結束，此前他就表示不確定今夏是否留隊，如今最終落定轉會馬體會。<br />\n<br />\n　　馬體會今夏投資驚人，球隊已經簽下了菲歷斯（J.Felix）和馬基斯-洛蘭迪（M.Llorente）等強人。查比亞加盟後，馬體會今夏的收購花費將突破1.7億英鎊。"},{"pid":"a3e2e1329244dff918746c2540c732bef112d21f","tid":1327820,"uid":3363,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:00:23.000Z","msg":"英人2000萬磅？<br />\n即係原本身價係0？"},{"pid":"129e6aeb5c01ff373dc07a2bd872ac1f4b4a033a","tid":1327820,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3e2e1329244dff918746c2540c732bef112d21f","tid":1327820,"uid":3363,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:00:23.000Z","msg":"英人2000萬磅？<br />\n即係原本身價係0？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:15:54.000Z","msg":"本身負身價<br />\n馬體會做水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e8